ygData.subject: Re: Lute of the Gypsy Princess
ygData.msgSnippet: A level 40 bard I work with says that the lute actually does have an increased effect over a regular lute. It might be only effective at higher levels, though.
ygData.messageBody:
A level 40 bard I work with says that the lute actually does have an
increased effect over a regular lute. It might be only effective at higher
levels, though.

Good Journey,

Sineras Silverlyre (Cazic-Thule)
